855
00:44:03,907 --> 00:44:06,603
"this rebellion in Massachusetts

856
00:44:06,677 --> 00:44:10,135
if you will grant
our freedom in return."

857
00:44:10,214 --> 00:44:12,045
GATES: Harry joined
a loyalist regiment

858
00:44:12,116 --> 00:44:13,981
called the Black Pioneers,

859
00:44:14,051 --> 00:44:16,645
and he wasn't the only one.

860
00:44:16,720 --> 00:44:21,316
Roughly 20,000 slaves
ran away to the British lines,

861
00:44:21,392 --> 00:44:23,952
far more than joined
the patriot cause.

862
00:44:24,028 --> 00:44:27,623
There were a lot of Harry
Washingtons in the British army.

863
00:44:27,698 --> 00:44:30,462
In fact, it's probably
fair to say that especially

864
00:44:30,534 --> 00:44:32,092
in the southern colonies,

865
00:44:32,169 --> 00:44:34,262
the British army effort
could not have been

866
00:44:34,338 --> 00:44:36,397
as successful as it was
for a time

867
00:44:36,473 --> 00:44:38,805
without the assistance
