918
00:47:21,071 --> 00:47:24,734
The whole thing is
built upon slavery.

919
00:47:24,808 --> 00:47:26,002
That's why they didn't
abolish it.

920
00:47:28,045 --> 00:47:30,343
GATES, VOICE-OVER: Slavery was
a part of American society

921
00:47:30,414 --> 00:47:32,245
from the very beginning.

922
00:47:32,316 --> 00:47:34,511
When the Declaration of
Independence was signed,

923
00:47:34,585 --> 00:47:38,578
slavery was legal in each
