942
00:48:46,890 --> 00:48:50,758
In essence, this was
the epicenter of slavery

943
00:48:50,827 --> 00:48:51,851
in the New World.

944
00:48:54,798 --> 00:49:00,327
But in August of 1791,
this colony began to collapse

945
00:49:00,404 --> 00:49:04,397
as the slaves rose up against
their hated masters.

946
00:49:08,712 --> 00:49:12,876
Inspired by the same ideals
as the American patriots,

947
00:49:12,950 --> 00:49:18,149
they fought off European armies
