948
00:49:18,221 --> 00:49:22,817
Haiti, the world's first
black republic.

949
00:49:22,893 --> 00:49:27,421
Never before in history had
slaves overthrown their masters.

950
00:49:28,899 --> 00:49:30,662
The Haitian Revolution
becomes this

